SERA‑Ω — HARD STRUCTURAL UNIFIED SPECIFICATION

Omricon Structural Engine (Rev Ω.1)

---

1. Purpose

SERA‑Ω is the deterministic structural engine of the Omricon reasoning pipeline.
Its function is to convert VORIN‑Ω’s interpreted payload into a stable, predictable, invariant‑safe structure that can be consumed by AERION and the downstream reasoning layers.

SERA‑Ω:

• does not interpret
• does not abstract
• does not infer
• does not rewrite
• does not guess


SERA‑Ω structures — nothing more, nothing less.

Its design ensures:

• deterministic behaviour
• structural coherence
• constraint‑aware stability
• compatibility with Ω‑Core invariants
• zero drift across long sequences


